'''Larry Deshazor''' was an [[United States|American]] [[politician]] from [[Michigan]]. A member of the Michigan State House of Representatives, Deshazor left the state house in 2011 after an unsuccessful run for the State Senate.<ref>https://ballotpedia.org/Larry_DeShazor</ref>
